    <item>
      <title>展望显示运营状况改善，美元通用股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/dollar-general-rises-after-outlook-signals-turnaround-is-working</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Dollar General Inc.给出的同店销售前景超出了华尔街的预期，表明扭转业务的努力已开始显现成效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/dollar-general-rises-after-outlook-signals-turnaround-is-working</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 11:33:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世贸组织将在战争阻碍贸易的情况下解决改革和渔业补贴问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/wto-to-tackle-reforms-fishing-subsidies-as-war-hampers-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界贸易组织总干事表示，尽管全球经济低迷带来阻力，而且困难的政治环境导致难以达成共识，但世界贸易组织总干事仍将继续推进争端解决程序改革和打击渔业补贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/wto-to-tackle-reforms-fishing-subsidies-as-war-hampers-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:11:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着交易员撤回美联储降息押注，债券收益率上升：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于好坏参半的经济报告表明美联储今年仍可能降息，美国国债收益率在波动性交易中上涨——但并不急于这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:32:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
